If you want to avoid blocking the initiator thread, e.g. because its the event dispatch thread, submit the entire operation to a background thread:

```java
CompletableFuture&lt;Void&gt; operation = CompletableFuture.runAsync(() -&gt; {
  mainMap.forEach(1, (k, v) -&gt; {
    System.out.println(&quot;Object &quot; + k
