`main` has to be static. static is more or less an advanced concept; if you don&#39;t want to learn about it yet (probably a good idea), the fix is simple: Get out of `static` IMMEDIATELY. This is not difficult:

```
public class MyApp {
  public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {
    new MyApp().go();
  }

  void go() throws Exception {
    // this is where you write your code
  }
}
```

